  <brief_title>To Evaluate the Impact of Treatment Interruption on Re-initiation of Bifeprunox</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Single-center Safety and Tolerability Study to Evaluate the Impact of Treatment Interruption on Re-initiation of Bifeprunox in Subjects With Schizophrenia or Schizoaffective Disorder</official_title>
