  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate a safe treatment interruption interval(s) for
      re-initiation of bifeprunox at a therapeutic dose. The study duration is approximately 7 to
      10 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
